      <data key="d7">ENGINEERING CONTROLS FOR AIRBORNE PATHOGENS</data>
      <data key="d8">PUBMED PMID 32218911</data>
      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">The PubMed study (PMID 32218911) is a potential source of validation evidence for the effectiveness and operational parameters of the engineering controls; consulting the full paper can provide measured outcomes.</data>
