      <data key="d8">CARBON DIOXIDE</data>
      <data key="d9">HAS_DOSE</data>
      <data key="d10">CO2 concentration functions as a measurable operating parameter used to specify and monitor ventilation performance (i.e., steady-state or transient ppm values reflect balance of occupancy CO2 generation and outdoor air exchange).</data>
