      <data key="d10">Ventilation strategies are implemented within inpatient wards to alter airflow patterns, increase dilution and removal of aerosols, and reduce airborne exposure risk. Effectiveness depends on HVAC configuration, room geometry and occupancy.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.95</data>
      <data key="d12">1</data>
