      <data key="d9">TARGETS</data>
      <data key="d10">Ventilation modifications are aimed at reducing airborne dispersion and cross-exposure of MERS-CoV by diluting and removing virus-laden aerosols and changing transport paths in clinical settings.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.9</data>
