      <data key="d9">VALIDATED_BY</data>
      <data key="d10">CFD and particle simulations in commuter buses validate how ventilation patterns influence spatial exposure gradients and hotspots, supporting ventilation strategy design.</data>
      <data key="d11">0.82</data>
